{
  "video_id": "493uXtbp95Q",
  "title": "The First Lady on the Importance of Studying Abroad",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 1000.0,
      "text": "The First Lady: (applause) Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 1000.0,
      "end_time": 2000.0,
      "text": "Well, ni-hao."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 2000.0,
      "end_time": 6734.0,
      "text": "(laughter) It is such a pleasure and an honor to"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 6734.0,
      "end_time": 11834.0,
      "text": "be here with all of you at this great university, so"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 11834.0,
      "end_time": 14233.0,
      "text": "thank you so much for having me."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 14233.0,
      "end_time": 18233.0,
      "text": "Now, before I get started today, on behalf of myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 18233.0,
      "end_time": 21567.0,
      "text": "and my husband, I just want to say a few very"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 21567.0,
      "end_time": 24633.0,
      "text": "brief words about Malaysia Airlines Flight 370."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 24633.0,
      "end_time": 27500.0,
      "text": "As my husband has said, the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 27500.0,
      "end_time": 30033.0,
      "text": "is offering as many resources as possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 30033.0,
      "end_time": 32533.0,
      "text": "to assist in the search."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 32533.0,
      "end_time": 36700.0,
      "text": "And please know that we are keeping all of the"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 36700.0,
      "end_time": 40200.0,
      "text": "families and loved ones of those on this flight"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40200.0,
      "end_time": 42633.0,
      "text": "in our thoughts and prayers at this"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 42633.0,
      "end_time": 45567.0,
      "text": "very difficult time."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 45567.0,
      "end_time": 50400.0,
      "text": "Now with that, I want to start by recognizing our"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50400.0,
      "end_time": 55000.0,
      "text": "new Ambassador to China, Ambassador Baucus;"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55000.0,
      "end_time": 58967.0,
      "text": "President Wang; Chairman Zhu; Vice President Li;"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58967.0,
      "end_time": 63066.0,
      "text": "Director Cueller; Professor Oi, and the"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63066.0,
      "end_time": 66734.0,
      "text": "Stanford Center; President Sexton from New York"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66734.0,
      "end_time": 69600.0,
      "text": "University, which is an excellent study abroad"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69600.0,
      "end_time": 73633.0,
      "text": "program in Shanghai; and John Thornton,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73633.0,
      "end_time": 76667.0,
      "text": "Director of the Global Leadership Program"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76667.0,
      "end_time": 78734.0,
      "text": "at Tsinghua University."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78734.0,
      "end_time": 81100.0,
      "text": "Thank you all for joining us."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81100.0,
      "end_time": 85567.0,
      "text": "But most of all, I want to thank all of the students"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 85567.0,
      "end_time": 86700.0,
      "text": "who are here today."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 86700.0,
      "end_time": 90633.0,
      "text": "And I particularly want to thank Eric Schaefer"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90633.0,
      "end_time": 94800.0,
      "text": "and Zhu Xuanhao for that extraordinary English"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94800.0,
      "end_time": 96133.0,
      "text": "and Chinese introduction."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 96133.0,
      "end_time": 102033.0,
      "text": "That was a powerful symbol of everything that"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102033.0,
      "end_time": 104867.0,
      "text": "I want to talk with you about today."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 104867.0,
      "end_time": 107333.0,
      "text": "See, by learning each other's languages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 107333.0,
      "end_time": 112200.0,
      "text": "and by showing such curiosity and respect for each other's"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 112200.0,
      "end_time": 116800.0,
      "text": "cultures, Mr. Schafer and Ms. Zhu"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116800.0,
      "end_time": 120166.0,
      "text": "and all of you are building bridges of understanding that"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 120166.0,
      "end_time": 122400.0,
      "text": "will lead to so much more."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 122400.0,
      "end_time": 126100.0,
      "text": "And I'm here today because I know that our future"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 126100.0,
      "end_time": 128934.0,
      "text": "depends on connections like these among"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 128934.0,
      "end_time": 132100.0,
      "text": "young people like you across the globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 132100.0,
      "end_time": 135734.0,
      "text": "That's why when my husband and I travel abroad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 135734.0,
      "end_time": 139000.0,
      "text": "we don't just visit palaces and parliaments"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 139000.0,
      "end_time": 141567.0,
      "text": "and meet with heads of state."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141567.0,
      "end_time": 144600.0,
      "text": "We also come to schools like this one to meet"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 144600.0,
      "end_time": 147967.0,
      "text": "with students like you, because we believe that"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 147967.0,
      "end_time": 150867.0,
      "text": "relationships between nations aren't just about"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 150867.0,
      "end_time": 154834.0,
      "text": "relationships between governments or leaders --"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 154834.0,
      "end_time": 157166.0,
      "text": "they're about relationships between"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 157166.0,
      "end_time": 161367.0,
      "text": "people, particularly young people."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 161367.0,
      "end_time": 164166.0,
      "text": "So we view study abroad programs not just"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 164166.0,
      "end_time": 167100.0,
      "text": "as an educational opportunity for students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167100.0,
      "end_time": 174133.0,
      "text": "but also as a vital part of America's foreign policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 174133.0,
      "end_time": 176433.0,
      "text": "Through the wonders of modern technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176433.0,
      "end_time": 180333.0,
      "text": "our world is more connected than ever before."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 180333.0,
      "end_time": 182834.0,
      "text": "Ideas can cross oceans with the click"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 182834.0,
      "end_time": 184333.0,
      "text": "of a button."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 184333.0,
      "end_time": 187567.0,
      "text": "Companies can do business and compete with companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 187567.0,
      "end_time": 189467.0,
      "text": "across the globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 189467.0,
      "end_time": 192533.0,
      "text": "And we can text, email, Skype with people"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 192533.0,
      "end_time": 194467.0,
      "text": "on every continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 194467.0,
      "end_time": 197700.0,
      "text": "So studying abroad isn't just a fun way to spend a"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 197700.0,
      "end_time": 201567.0,
      "text": "semester; it is quickly becoming the key to"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 201567.0,
      "end_time": 204867.0,
      "text": "success in our global economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 204867.0,
      "end_time": 207300.0,
      "text": "Because getting ahead in today's workplaces isn't"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 207300.0,
      "end_time": 210533.0,
      "text": "just about getting good grades or test scores"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 210533.0,
      "end_time": 215367.0,
      "text": "in school, which are important."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 215367.0,
      "end_time": 218667.0,
      "text": "It's also about having real experience with the"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 218667.0,
      "end_time": 221734.0,
      "text": "world beyond your borders -- experience with"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 221734.0,
      "end_time": 225000.0,
      "text": "languages, cultures and societies very different"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 225000.0,
      "end_time": 226700.0,
      "text": "from your own."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 226700.0,
      "end_time": 230300.0,
      "text": "Or, as the Chinese saying goes: \"It is better"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 230300.0,
      "end_time": 232967.0,
      "text": "to travel ten thousand miles than to read"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 232967.0,
      "end_time": 235100.0,
      "text": "ten thousand books.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 235100.0,
      "end_time": 237867.0,
      "text": "But let's be clear, studying abroad is about"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 237867.0,
      "end_time": 241533.0,
      "text": "so much more than improving your own future."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 241533.0,
      "end_time": 244000.0,
      "text": "It's also about shaping the future of your"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 244000.0,
      "end_time": 248100.0,
      "text": "countries and of the world we all share."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 248100.0,
      "end_time": 250633.0,
      "text": "Because when it comes to the defining challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 250633.0,
      "end_time": 253533.0,
      "text": "of our time -- whether it's climate change"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 253533.0,
      "end_time": 257533.0,
      "text": "or economic opportunity or the spread of nuclear weapons --"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 257533.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261200.00000000003,
      "text": "these are shared challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 261200.0,
      "end_time": 265033.0,
      "text": "And no one country can confront them alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 265033.0,
      "end_time": 268333.0,
      "text": "The only way forward is together."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 268333.0,
      "end_time": 270734.0,
      "text": "That's why it is so important for young people"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 270734.0,
      "end_time": 275233.0,
      "text": "like you to live and study in each other's countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 275233.0,
      "end_time": 277433.0,
      "text": "because that's how you develop"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 277433.0,
      "end_time": 280066.0,
      "text": "that habit of cooperation."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 280066.0,
      "end_time": 282867.0,
      "text": "You do it by immersing yourself in one another's"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 282867.0,
      "end_time": 287467.0,
      "text": "culture, by learning each other's stories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 287467.0,
      "end_time": 289700.0,
      "text": "by getting past the stereotypes"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 289700.0,
      "end_time": 294367.0,
      "text": "and misconceptions that too often divide us."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 294367.0,
      "end_time": 295867.0,
      "text": "That's how you come to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 295867.0,
      "end_time": 298066.0,
      "text": "how much we all share."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 298066.0,
      "end_time": 300467.0,
      "text": "That's how you realize that we all have"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 300467.0,
      "end_time": 305867.0,
      "text": "a stake in each other's success -- that cures discovered here"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 305867.0,
      "end_time": 309767.0,
      "text": "in Beijing could save lives in America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 309767.0,
      "end_time": 312767.0,
      "text": "that clean energy technologies from Silicon Valley"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 312767.0,
      "end_time": 315433.0,
      "text": "in California could improve the environment here"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 315433.0,
      "end_time": 317667.0,
      "text": "in China, that the architecture"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 317667.0,
      "end_time": 321367.0,
      "text": "of an ancient temple in Xi'an could inspire the design"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 321367.0,
      "end_time": 325934.0,
      "text": "of new buildings in Dallas or Detroit."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 325934.0,
      "end_time": 329066.0,
      "text": "And that's when the connections you make"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 329066.0,
      "end_time": 332166.0,
      "text": "as classmates or labmates can blossom"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 332166.0,
      "end_time": 334700.0,
      "text": "into something more."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 334700.0,
      "end_time": 338200.0,
      "text": "That's what happened when Abigail Coplin became"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 338200.0,
      "end_time": 342166.0,
      "text": "an American Fulbright Scholar here at Peking University."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 342166.0,
      "end_time": 345467.0,
      "text": "She and her colleagues published papers together"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 345467.0,
      "end_time": 348834.0,
      "text": "in top science journals, and they built research"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 348834.0,
      "end_time": 351800.0,
      "text": "partnerships that lasted long after they returned"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 351800.0,
      "end_time": 354266.0,
      "text": "to their home countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 354266.0,
      "end_time": 357300.0,
      "text": "And Professor Niu Ke from Peking University"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 357300.0,
      "end_time": 360367.0,
      "text": "was a Fulbright Scholarship --"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 360367.0,
      "end_time": 364700.0,
      "text": "Scholar in the U.S. last year, and he reported -- and"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 364700.0,
      "end_time": 367000.0,
      "text": "this is a quote from him -- he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 367000.0,
      "end_time": 369834.0,
      "text": "\"The most memorable experiences were"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 369834.0,
      "end_time": 373367.0,
      "text": "with my American friends.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 373367.0,
      "end_time": 377567.0,
      "text": "These lasting bonds represent the true value"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 377567.0,
      "end_time": 379800.0,
      "text": "of studying abroad."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 379800.0,
      "end_time": 382533.0,
      "text": "And I am thrilled that more and more students"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 382533.0,
      "end_time": 384800.0,
      "text": "are getting this opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 384800.0,
      "end_time": 388166.0,
      "text": "As you've heard, China is currently the fifth most"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 388166.0,
      "end_time": 392700.0,
      "text": "popular destination for Americans studying abroad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 392700.0,
      "end_time": 395333.0,
      "text": "and today, the highest number of exchange"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 395333.0,
      "end_time": 396734.0,
      "text": "students in the U.S."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 396734.0,
      "end_time": 399166.0,
      "text": "are from China."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 399166.0,
      "end_time": 403033.0,
      "text": "But still, too many students never have this"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 403033.0,
      "end_time": 410600.0,
      "text": "chance, and some that do are hesitant to take it."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 410600.0,
      "end_time": 413600.0,
      "text": "They may feel like studying abroad is only"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 413600.0,
      "end_time": 417000.0,
      "text": "for wealthy students or students from certain"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 417000.0,
      "end_time": 418467.0,
      "text": "kinds of universities."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 418467.0,
      "end_time": 421967.0,
      "text": "Or they may think to themselves, well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 421967.0,
      "end_time": 427133.0,
      "text": "that sounds fun but how will it be useful in my life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 427133.0,
      "end_time": 428600.0,
      "text": "And believe me, I understand where these"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 428600.0,
      "end_time": 431233.0,
      "text": "young people are coming from because"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 431233.0,
      "end_time": 435367.0,
      "text": "I felt the same way back when I was in college."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 435367.0,
      "end_time": 438467.0,
      "text": "See, I came from a working-class family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 438467.0,
      "end_time": 443734.0,
      "text": "and it never occurred to me to study abroad -- never."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 443734.0,
      "end_time": 447433.0,
      "text": "My parents didn't get a chance to attend college,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 447433.0,
      "end_time": 450700.0,
      "text": "so I was focused on getting into a university,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 450700.0,
      "end_time": 453700.0,
      "text": "earning my degree so that I could get a good job"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 453700.0,
      "end_time": 457133.0,
      "text": "to support myself and help my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 457133.0,
      "end_time": 460500.0,
      "text": "And I know for a lot of young people like me who"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 460500.0,
      "end_time": 463667.0,
      "text": "are struggling to afford a regular semester"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 463667.0,
      "end_time": 467467.0,
      "text": "of school, paying for plane tickets or living expenses"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 467467.0,
      "end_time": 471233.0,
      "text": "halfway around the world just isn't possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 471233.0,
      "end_time": 476266.0,
      "text": "And that's not acceptable, because study abroad"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 476266.0,
      "end_time": 478033.0,
      "text": "shouldn't just be for students"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 478033.0,
      "end_time": 480300.0,
      "text": "from certain backgrounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 480300.0,
      "end_time": 485166.0,
      "text": "Our hope is to build connections between people"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 485166.0,
      "end_time": 489600.0,
      "text": "of all races and socioeconomic backgrounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 489600.0,
      "end_time": 497000.0,
      "text": "because it is that diversity that truly will"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 497000.0,
      "end_time": 503433.0,
      "text": "change the face of our relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 503433.0,
      "end_time": 507300.0,
      "text": "So we believe that diversity makes our"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 507300.0,
      "end_time": 510600.0,
      "text": "country vibrant and strong."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 510600.0,
      "end_time": 513367.0,
      "text": "And our study abroad programs should reflect"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 513366.99999999994,
      "end_time": 518666.99999999994,
      "text": "the true spirit of America to the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 518667.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521500.00000000006,
      "text": "And that's why when my husband visited China"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 521500.0,
      "end_time": 528767.0,
      "text": "back in 2009, he announced the 100,000 Strong initiative"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 528767.0,
      "end_time": 530767.0,
      "text": "to increase the number and diversity"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 530767.0,
      "end_time": 533967.0,
      "text": "of American students studying in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 533967.0,
      "end_time": 537567.0,
      "text": "And this year, as we mark the 35th anniversary"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 537567.0,
      "end_time": 540300.0,
      "text": "of the normalization of relationships between"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 540300.0,
      "end_time": 542000.0,
      "text": "our two countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 542000.0,
      "end_time": 545467.0,
      "text": "the U.S. government actually supports more American"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 545467.0,
      "end_time": 549367.0,
      "text": "students in China than in any other country"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 549367.0,
      "end_time": 551266.0,
      "text": "in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 551266.0,
      "end_time": 554734.0,
      "text": "We are sending high school, college and"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 554734.0,
      "end_time": 558133.0,
      "text": "graduate students here to study Chinese."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 558133.0,
      "end_time": 560100.0,
      "text": "We're inviting teachers from China"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 560100.0,
      "end_time": 563100.0,
      "text": "to teach Mandarin in American schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 563100.0,
      "end_time": 565500.0,
      "text": "We're providing free online advising"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 565500.0,
      "end_time": 568166.0,
      "text": "for students in China who want to study"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 568166.0,
      "end_time": 572100.0,
      "text": "in the U.S. And the U.S.-China Fulbright program"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 572100.0,
      "end_time": 578233.0,
      "text": "is still going strong with more than 3,000 alumni."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 578233.0,
      "end_time": 581667.0,
      "text": "And the private sector is stepping up as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 581667.0,
      "end_time": 585233.0,
      "text": "For example, Steve Schwarzman, who is the"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 585233.0,
      "end_time": 588233.0,
      "text": "head of an American company called Blackstone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 588233.0,
      "end_time": 591400.0,
      "text": "is funding a new program at Tsinghua University"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 591400.0,
      "end_time": 593800.0,
      "text": "modeled on the Rhodes Scholarship."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 593800.0,
      "end_time": 596000.0,
      "text": "And today, students from all kinds"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 596000.0,
      "end_time": 599967.0,
      "text": "of backgrounds are studying here in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 599967.0,
      "end_time": 603367.0,
      "text": "Take the example of Royale Nicholson,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 603367.0,
      "end_time": 605800.0,
      "text": "who's from Cleveland, Ohio."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 605800.0,
      "end_time": 607767.0,
      "text": "She attends New York University's"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 607767.0,
      "end_time": 610200.0,
      "text": "program in Shanghai."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 610200.0,
      "end_time": 614100.0,
      "text": "Now, like me, Royale is a first-generation"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 614100.0,
      "end_time": 616233.0,
      "text": "college student."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 616233.0,
      "end_time": 618967.0,
      "text": "And her mother worked two full-time jobs while"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 618967.0,
      "end_time": 623233.0,
      "text": "her father worked nights to support their family."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 623233.0,
      "end_time": 626767.0,
      "text": "And of her experience in Shanghai, Royale said --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 626767.0,
      "end_time": 628834.0,
      "text": "and this is her quote -- she said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 628834.0,
      "end_time": 634266.0,
      "text": "\"This city oozes persistence and inspires me to accomplish"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 634266.0,
      "end_time": 636600.0,
      "text": "all that I can.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 636600.0,
      "end_time": 637767.0,
      "text": "And happy birthday, Royale."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 637767.0,
      "end_time": 638967.0,
      "text": "It was her birthday yesterday."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 638967.0,
      "end_time": 641233.0,
      "text": "(Laughter.)"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 641233.0,
      "end_time": 645266.0,
      "text": "And then there's Philmon Haile from"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 645266.0,
      "end_time": 648433.0,
      "text": "the University of Washington, whose family came"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 648433.0,
      "end_time": 654400.0,
      "text": "to the U.S. as refugees from Eritrea when he was a child."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 654400.0,
      "end_time": 656600.0,
      "text": "And of his experience studying in China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 656600.0,
      "end_time": 660300.0,
      "text": "he said, \"Study abroad is a powerful vehicle"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 660300.0,
      "end_time": 663667.0,
      "text": "for people-to-people exchange as we move into"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 663667.0,
      "end_time": 668934.0,
      "text": "a new era of citizen diplomacy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 668934.0,
      "end_time": 671700.0,
      "text": "\"A new era of citizen diplomacy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 671700.0,
      "end_time": 674266.0,
      "text": "I could not have said it better myself, because"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 674266.0,
      "end_time": 677233.0,
      "text": "that's really what I'm talking about."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 677233.0,
      "end_time": 681433.0,
      "text": "I am talking about ordinary citizens reaching"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 681433.0,
      "end_time": 683567.0,
      "text": "out to the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 683567.0,
      "end_time": 688233.0,
      "text": "And as I always tell young people back in America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 688233.0,
      "end_time": 690934.0,
      "text": "you don't need to get on a plane"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 690934.0,
      "end_time": 693834.0,
      "text": "to be a citizen diplomat."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 693834.0,
      "end_time": 697867.0,
      "text": "I tell them that if you have an Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 697867.0,
      "end_time": 701433.0,
      "text": "connection in your home, school, or library, within"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 701433.0,
      "end_time": 704533.0,
      "text": "seconds you can be transported anywhere"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 704533.0,
      "end_time": 708800.0,
      "text": "in the world and meet people on every continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 708800.0,
      "end_time": 712800.0,
      "text": "And that's why I'm posting a daily travel blog"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 712800.0,
      "end_time": 716867.0,
      "text": "with videos and photos of my experiences here in China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 716867.0,
      "end_time": 720266.0,
      "text": "because I want young people in America"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 720266.0,
      "end_time": 723500.0,
      "text": "to be part of this visit."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 723500.0,
      "end_time": 728667.0,
      "text": "And that's really the power of technology --"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 728667.0,
      "end_time": 733467.0,
      "text": "how it can open up the entire world and expose"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 733467.0,
      "end_time": 737533.0,
      "text": "us to ideas and innovations we never could have imagined."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 737533.0,
      "end_time": 739767.0,
      "text": "And that's why it's so important for information"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 739767.0,
      "end_time": 743266.0,
      "text": "and ideas to flow freely over the Internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 743266.0,
      "end_time": 745400.0,
      "text": "and through the media, because that's"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 745400.0,
      "end_time": 747667.0,
      "text": "how we discover the truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 747667.0,
      "end_time": 749834.0,
      "text": "That's how we learn what's really happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 749834.0,
      "end_time": 753767.0,
      "text": "in our communities and our country and our world."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 753767.0,
      "end_time": 757233.0,
      "text": "And that's how we decide which values and ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 757233.0,
      "end_time": 760266.0,
      "text": "we think are best -- by questioning and debating"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 760266.0,
      "end_time": 763934.0,
      "text": "them vigorously, by listening to all sides"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 763934.0,
      "end_time": 767367.0,
      "text": "of an argument, and by judging for ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 767367.0,
      "end_time": 772066.0,
      "text": "And believe me, I know how this can be a messy"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 772066.0,
      "end_time": 774233.0,
      "text": "and frustrating process."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 774233.0,
      "end_time": 776166.0,
      "text": "My husband and I are on the receiving"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 776166.0,
      "end_time": 779367.0,
      "text": "end of plenty of questioning and criticism from our media"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 779367.0,
      "end_time": 781700.0,
      "text": "and our fellow citizens."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 781700.0,
      "end_time": 785400.0,
      "text": "And it's not always easy, but we wouldn't trade"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 785400.0,
      "end_time": 788033.0,
      "text": "it for anything in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 788033.0,
      "end_time": 789867.0,
      "text": "Because time and again, we have seen that"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 789867.0,
      "end_time": 793100.0,
      "text": "countries are stronger and more prosperous when"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 793100.0,
      "end_time": 796400.0,
      "text": "the voices of and opinions of all their citizens"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 796400.0,
      "end_time": 797967.0,
      "text": "can be heard."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 797967.0,
      "end_time": 800233.0,
      "text": "And as my husband has said, we respect"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 800233.0,
      "end_time": 802667.0,
      "text": "the uniqueness of other cultures and societies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 802667.0,
      "end_time": 805400.0,
      "text": "but when it comes to expressing yourself freely"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 805400.0,
      "end_time": 808066.0,
      "text": "and worshipping as you choose and having open"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 808066.0,
      "end_time": 811567.0,
      "text": "access to information, we believe those universal"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 811567.0,
      "end_time": 814166.0,
      "text": "rights -- they are universal rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 814166.0,
      "end_time": 818400.0,
      "text": "that are the birthright of every person on this planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 818400.0,
      "end_time": 821033.0,
      "text": "We believe that all people deserve the opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 821033.0,
      "end_time": 824367.0,
      "text": "to fulfill their highest potential as I was able"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 824367.0,
      "end_time": 828467.0,
      "text": "to do in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 828467.0,
      "end_time": 831867.0,
      "text": "And as you learn about new cultures and form new"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 831867.0,
      "end_time": 835767.0,
      "text": "friendships during your time here in China"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 835767.0,
      "end_time": 841300.0,
      "text": "and in the United States, all of you are the living,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 841300.0,
      "end_time": 845800.0,
      "text": "breathing embodiment of those values."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 845800.0,
      "end_time": 848633.0,
      "text": "So I guarantee you that in studying abroad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 848633.0,
      "end_time": 853467.0,
      "text": "you're not just changing your own life, you are changing the"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 853467.0,
      "end_time": 856500.0,
      "text": "lives of everyone you meet."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 856500.0,
      "end_time": 858300.0,
      "text": "And as the great American President"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 858300.0,
      "end_time": 861100.0,
      "text": "John F. Kennedy once said about foreign students studying"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 861100.0,
      "end_time": 864667.0,
      "text": "in the U.S., he said \"I think they teach"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 864667.0,
      "end_time": 867300.0,
      "text": "more than they learn.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 867300.0,
      "end_time": 870200.0,
      "text": "And that is just as true of young Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 870200.0,
      "end_time": 872700.0,
      "text": "who study abroad."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 872700.0,
      "end_time": 876033.0,
      "text": "All of you are America's best face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 876033.0,
      "end_time": 881166.0,
      "text": "and China's best face, to the world -- you truly are."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 881166.0,
      "end_time": 884800.0,
      "text": "Every day, you show the world your countries'"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 884800.0,
      "end_time": 890333.0,
      "text": "energy and creativity and optimism and unwavering"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 890333.0,
      "end_time": 893767.0,
      "text": "belief in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 893767.0,
      "end_time": 897200.0,
      "text": "And every day, you remind us -- and me in particular"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 897200.0,
      "end_time": 901200.0,
      "text": "-- of just how much we can achieve if we reach"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 901200.0,
      "end_time": 907633.0,
      "text": "across borders, and learn to see ourselves in each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 907633.0,
      "end_time": 910467.0,
      "text": "and confront our shared challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 910467.0,
      "end_time": 913133.0,
      "text": "with shared resolve."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 913133.0,
      "end_time": 916133.0,
      "text": "So I hope you all will keep seeking"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 916133.0,
      "end_time": 919467.0,
      "text": "these kinds of experiences."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 919467.0,
      "end_time": 922400.0,
      "text": "And I hope you'll keep teaching each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 922400.0,
      "end_time": 925033.0,
      "text": "and learning from each other, and building bonds"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 925033.0,
      "end_time": 928100.0,
      "text": "of friendship that will enrich your lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 928100.0,
      "end_time": 931600.0,
      "text": "and enrich our world for decades to come."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 931600.0,
      "end_time": 934500.0,
      "text": "You all have so much to offer, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 934500.0,
      "end_time": 937367.0,
      "text": "I cannot wait to see all that you achieve together"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 937367.0,
      "end_time": 938600.0,
      "text": "in the years ahead."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 938600.0,
      "end_time": 939734.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 939734.0,
      "end_time": 943467.0,
      "text": "Xie-Xie."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 943467.0,
      "end_time": 953467.0,
      "text": "(applause)"
    }
  ]
